{"word":"G2523 - καθίζω - kathízō - kath-id'-zo - Continue","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καθίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kathízō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kath-id'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Continue</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - உட்கார், வீற்றிரு, உட்கார்ந்திரு"},{"paragraph":"1. to make to sit down to set"},{"paragraph":"2. to sit down"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Another (active) form for <a href=\"#/G2516 - καθέζομαι - kathézomai - kath-ed'-zom-ahee/2516\">G2516</a>; to <i>seat down</i>, that is, <i>set</i> (figuratively <i>appoint</i>); intransitively to <i>sit</i> (down); figuratively to <i>settle</i> (<i>hover</i>, <i>dwell</i>): - continue, set, sit (down), tarry.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2516/2516\">G2516</a>, <a href=\"#/G2521/2521\">G2521</a>, <a href=\"#/G2523/2523\">G2523</a>"}]}